<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: right;"><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;"><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Charter<font size="4">ed By&nbsp;</font>The British Schools&nbsp;<font size="4">Founda<font size="4">t<font size="4">ion</font></font></font><br></i></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="1"><i><br></i></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" style=""><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"></font></div><span lang="en-GB" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: start;"><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font color="#000000"><br></font><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Another week has raced by as we continue to work hard to establish the new school campus. Each day that passes new things get added and the campus continues to come to life.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><u></u>&nbsp;<u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">On Wednesday, Andrew Fitzmaurice the Chief Executive Officer for Nord Anglia Education and Shaun Williams took time out from their busy schedules to visit the new campus. As well as talking to the staff, they also had a tour of the school and met teachers and students in their short time. Andrew visits many schools around the world and he was very impressed with the amount of work and the progress made to get the school to opening.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><u></u>&nbsp;<u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">A number of parents have asked me about the possibility of using the bus service. If you wish to enroll for the bus service, please come in to school and speak with Ms Olivia our bus manager to get a form to complete. You will need to have signed up by the 7<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;September. The service will start for any extra students from Monday 10<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;September.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><u></u>&nbsp;<u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Thank you to all families that attended the curriculum presentations on Monday. We sincerely hope that you found the information useful. It is always very difficult to get a balance right between sections and departments. There are of course things that we can improve for next time and the feedback we have received will be considered very carefully.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><u></u>&nbsp;<u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">I have continued to receive lots of great feedback via email, informal conversations and in our suggestion box at reception. This has been very useful to me in discussing further improvements as the school moves forward. Please keep your comments coming, I welcome all comments and feedback at any time. On reflection I will keep the suggestion box at the reception desk for the whole year as it is proving to be a popular way of parents and families communicating with us.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><u></u>&nbsp;<u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">One area that I know we have to do more work on is the canteen. Currently we are in a temporary situation using the grand hall for the service. This has some limitations and is not great. It certainly is not how I wish to see our food service moving forward. I have a meeting with the canteen staff on Monday to discuss the menus, the variety and balance of food that we are offering. I am going to ask students and some teachers to join some discussion groups with the provider on this issue. I will keep you updated on what is very important issue for all concerned in the school.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><u></u>&nbsp;<u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">A big thank you again for your continued cooperation with the traffic which has been improving week on week. I shall continue to meet with the hospital management on a weekly basis and they appear to be content at the moment with the way things are set up. During the October half term we hope to improve both roads either side of the school building and include safer walkways for families and children.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><u></u>&nbsp;<u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">Finally, I wish you all a very relaxing weekend with your families.</p></div><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><u></u>&nbsp;<u></u></p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"><b><span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Paul Holyome</span></b><u></u><u></u></p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"><span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Principal</span></p><font color="#000000"><br><br></font></font></div></span><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style=""><i style=""><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600" style="" face="Arial, sans-serif"><b style="">World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font></div></div>]]></td>
